<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 18:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>东耶路撒冷居民在一月初西岸袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-attack-earlier-in-january/0000018d-4160-dc44-a5bf-c9f600be0000</link><description>42 岁的拉拉·坦努斯 (Lara Tannous) 医生在耶路撒冷一家医院担任药剂师。大约三周前，她在奥夫拉社区附近的约旦河西岸枪击事件中被枪杀，东耶路撒冷居民阿马尔·曼苏尔 (Amar Mansour)，32 岁也被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 17:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-attack-earlier-in-january/0000018d-4160-dc44-a5bf-c9f600be0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列“Fauda”明星在加沙受重伤，讲述爆炸事件，呼吁释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fauda-star-seriously-wounded-in-gaza-recounts-blast-calls-for-hostages-release/0000018d-40e3-dc44-a5bf-c8f781e80000</link><description>演员兼歌手伊丹·阿梅迪住院近三周，他在以色列主流新闻媒体现场直播的新闻发布会上表示，他希望尽快恢复表演和拍摄</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 16:09:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fauda-star-seriously-wounded-in-gaza-recounts-blast-calls-for-hostages-release/0000018d-40e3-dc44-a5bf-c8f781e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列摩萨德否认内塔尼亚胡盟友将司法改革抗议领导人与哈马斯联系起来的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/mossad-denies-netanyahu-allys-claims-about-judicial-overhaul-protester-links-with-hamas/0000018d-4015-dc44-a5bf-c8b74c940000</link><description>塔利·戈特利夫在社交媒体上发帖称，美国拦截了哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔与以色列政府反对者之间的通话，摩萨德已召集该反对者参加会议</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/mossad-denies-netanyahu-allys-claims-about-judicial-overhaul-protester-links-with-hamas/0000018d-4015-dc44-a5bf-c8b74c940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对周五国际法院对加沙种族灭绝指控的临时裁决有何期待？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/what-can-israel-expect-in-tomorrows-icj-interim-ruling-on-the-gaza-genocide-charge/0000018d-40bc-d35c-a39f-eafe6d450000</link><description>南非在国际法院指控以色列犯有种族灭绝罪。法院会要求立即停火吗？以色列官员会因煽动而受到惩罚吗？裁决将如何执行？</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/what-can-israel-expect-in-tomorrows-icj-interim-ruling-on-the-gaza-genocide-charge/0000018d-40bc-d35c-a39f-eafe6d450000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院裁决之前，以色列解密文件以证明其保护平民的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/ahead-of-icj-ruling-israel-declassifies-documents-to-prove-efforts-to-protect-civilians/0000018d-40d0-d35c-a39f-eadac21b0000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，在国际法院就南非对以色列提出的种族灭绝指控作出临时裁决的前一天，以色列解密文件以证明其意图</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:48:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/ahead-of-icj-ruling-israel-declassifies-documents-to-prove-efforts-to-protect-civilians/0000018d-40d0-d35c-a39f-eadac21b0000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列-哈马斯人质释放过程的关键问答：“辛瓦尔很高兴为释放囚犯而死”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/q-a-on-israel-hamas-hostage-release-process-sinwar-is-happy-to-die-to-free-prisoners/0000018d-40ab-d35c-a39f-eafb67aa0000</link><description>根据我与加沙哈马斯领导人间接谈判的经验，这是他的观点。但他也认为，战后他将走出隧道并继续掌权。以下是一些</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/q-a-on-israel-hamas-hostage-release-process-sinwar-is-happy-to-die-to-free-prisoners/0000018d-40ab-d35c-a39f-eafb67aa0000</guid></item><item><title>“你怎么能赢得一场强加给你的战争呢？”加沙日记作者与死亡作斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-can-you-win-a-war-that-was-forced-on-you-gaza-diarists-grapple-with-death/0000018d-3c42-d07d-a79d-fde766f10000</link><description>由于国际媒体基本上被禁止进入加沙地带，加沙作家正在出版战争日记并填补空白</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-can-you-win-a-war-that-was-forced-on-you-gaza-diarists-grapple-with-death/0000018d-3c42-d07d-a79d-fde766f10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家发现焦虑与低睾酮水平之间缺失联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</link><description>众所周知，雄性激素缺乏与焦虑有关，现在我们知道了其中的原因。如果你的老鼠患有麻痹性焦虑症，注射一针睾酮可能会给他带来奇迹，但在未来，这一发现提出了一种新方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</guid></item><item><title>先是拜登，现在是卡塔尔：内塔尼亚胡正在创造敌人，以使他的中东永远战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡称卡塔尔代表以色列人质的调解角色“有问题”，这将他的战时行为推向了新的低点——这对一个不理解“公共礼仪”或“接受责任”等术语的人来说是有道理的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:29:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</guid></item><item><title>柏林展览聚焦加沙最年轻的人质</title><link>http