bDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-your-right-a-massacre-site-oct-7-atrocities-tourists-are-inundating-southern-israel/0000018d-3b8c-d35c-a39f-bbdeb1de0000</guid></item><item><title>回到加沙边境失落的 70 年代以色列嬉皮士天堂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/back-to-the-70s-hippie-haven-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-3b24-d3a5-afdf-7f37f5190000</link><description>凯雷姆沙洛姆基布兹是左翼抗议和狂欢狂欢的温床。 Avihu Ronen 教授刚刚出版了一本书，回顾了他在那里的 11 年，并解释了为什么基布兹的精神在今天比以往任何时候都更加重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/back-to-the-70s-hippie-haven-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-3b24-d3a5-afdf-7f37f5190000</guid></item><item><title>法国告诉以色列，反对建立加沙边境缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/france-tells-israel-it-opposes-creation-of-gaza-border-buffer-zone/0000018d-3fa3-dc44-a5bf-bfb74d820000</link><description>在国防部长访问之后，法国官方消息人士称，该安全区旨在阻止恐怖分子渗透到以色列，这将使巴勒斯坦权力机构难以控制加沙</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:52:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/france-tells-israel-it-opposes-creation-of-gaza-border-buffer-zone/0000018d-3fa3-dc44-a5bf-bfb74d820000</guid></item><item><title>兼顾军事义务和财产法：以色列国防军预备役学生努力跟上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</link><description>随着以色列学年的开始，大学试图帮助从战争中退伍的学生补上他们错过的材料。然而，并不是每个人都能参加，有些参加的人也很难集中注意力。一位讲师表示，“显然他们正在付出代价”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长秘书尽管不符合标准但仍获得持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</link><description>为尼利·卡多什颁发执照的高级军官奥菲尔·布基 (Ofir Buki) 在签署请求几天后就晋升为指挥官</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：中央情报局局长将与摩萨德局长、埃及和卡塔尔同行会面，以达成新的人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</link><description>在黎巴嫩边境附近发现可疑人员的报告后，以色列国防军表示对该地区的扫描没有发现渗透的迹象 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队与杰宁当地武装部队之间发生武装冲突 ■ 以色列国防军正在调查近东救济工程处的袭击，称不是由于以色列国防军空袭或炮火造成的 ■ 国际法院将于周五发布裁决，南非外交部长预计将出席听证会 ■ 以色列消息人士称双方远未就新的人质协议达成一致 ■ 美国军方证实胡塞武装向悬挂美国国旗的船只开火</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 03:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</guid></item><item><title>艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫喜欢“将不同文化融合在一起”。他在葬礼上又做了一次</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</link><description>尽管下着雨，而且几乎一片漆黑，数百人——犹太人和阿拉伯人、宗教人士和世俗人士、年轻人和老年人——聚集在一起参加中士的葬礼。一等兵（后）艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫，自愿参加战斗并于周一在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 01:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军参谋长反击监察机构调查，凸显与内塔尼亚胡的紧张关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</link><description>哈莱维表示，国家审计长计划在战争仍在进行时调查以色列国防军的行为，这是史无前例的，这将阻止军队实现其目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 00:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</guid></item></channel></rss>